{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/aaronhma/awesome-tensorflow-js/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"13e07304-3712-5886-a0fd-aec760937ab7","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-tensorflowjs-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-tensorflowjs-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome tensorflowjs awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome TensorFlowJS <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p>TensorFlow.js is an open source software library to develop machine learning models in JavaScript, and use machine learning\n(training and inference) directly in the browser or Node.js.</p>\n<p>This list is a collection of the best <a href=\"https://www.tensorflow.org/js\">TensorFlow.js</a> tools, resources, videos and shiny things.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#learn\">Learn</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#documentation\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tutorials\">Tutorials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#modelsprojects\">Models/Projects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#papers\">Papers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#videos\">Videos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#books\">Books</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#blog--posts\">Blog &#x26; Posts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#powered-by-tensorflowjs\">Powered by TensorFlow.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#tools\">Tools</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#libraries\">Libraries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#toolsutilities\">Tools/Utilities</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#online-community\">Online Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#social-media\">Social Media</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#contributions\">Contributions</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"learn\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#learn\" aria-label=\"learn permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Learn</h2>\n<h3 id=\"documentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#documentation\" aria-label=\"documentation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C1